Package: tailscale-cli-helpers
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash (>= 4.0), jq, tailscale
Description: Bash/Zsh functions for easy SSH access to Tailscale nodes
 Provides convenient bash/zsh functions for SSH access to Tailscale nodes
 with hostname completion and fuzzy matching. Includes the 'ts' command
 for quick connections and smart host resolution.
 .
 Features:
  - Tab completion for Tailscale hostnames
  - Fuzzy hostname matching
  - Support for both bash and zsh
  - Automatic fallback to regular SSH for non-Tailscale hosts
  - MagicDNS support